{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_08_03",
  "title": "miho 3話 迫力のあるドリフトだったでしょう",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（mihoさんに病院まで乗せて行ってもらった後）\n（俺は風邪と診断され、静養するように言われてしまった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After miho drove me to the hospital）\n（I was diagnosed with a cold and told to rest.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 8.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "まったく。たまたま車があったから良かったものの\n倒れるまで体調不良を放置なんて、社会人失格ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly. It's a good thing we had the car‚\nbut neglecting your health until you collapse is unprofessional.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "他所では、マネージャーがアイドルを車で送迎するのに\n星見プロでは、アイドルがマネージャーを運ぶなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other places‚ managers drive the idols around‚\nbut at Hoshimi Pro‚ the idol carries the manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……貴方にとって運が良かったかは知りませんが\n私の運転で運ばれるなんて、お気の毒でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I don't know if you consider yourself lucky‚\nbut being transported by my driving‚ how unfortunate for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、そんなことは……\nmihoさんがいてくれて、助かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ it's not like that…\nI was saved because you were there‚ miho.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、撮影までに完治させていただければ結構ですが\nでは、今日のところは失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's fine as long as you fully recover by the shoot.\nThen‚ I'll take my leave for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Day of the shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.8000030518
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.9333363851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（運転大丈夫かな……mihoさんのことだから）\n（きっと最後はなんとかしてくれると思うんだけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I wonder if the driving will be okay… knowing miho‚）\n（I'm sure she'll find a way in the end.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "目線はこっちで、ポーズは……こうでしょうか\nいい感じですか？　ふふ、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eyes over here‚ and the pose… like this?\nDoes it look good? Hehe‚ thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "普段、車を運転するのか……？　ええ\nたまにレンタカーを借りて、走らせることはありますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I drive usually…? Yes.\nSometimes I rent a car and go for a drive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "夜に誰もいない道を飛ばすのは、気分がいいですね\nこんな素敵な車なら、もっと気持ちいいんでしょうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels good to speed down empty roads at night.\nThough it would feel even better in a wonderful car like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（あはは……物は言いようだな……こういう時の）\n（mihoさんのそつのなさは、いっそすがすがしいよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ahaha… she certainly has a way with words… in times like this‚）\n（miho's flawlessness is almost refreshing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "この後の運転も、とても楽しみにしていたんです\n……一緒に免許を取った友人に、自慢したいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been looking forward to the driving part as well.\n…I’d like to brag about it to the friend I got my license with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.5333361309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、あとは運転シーンの撮影だけだが……\nどうか事故だけは起こりませんように……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ only the driving scene left…\nPlease‚ just let there be no accidents…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3666748047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "あのコーナーはスピードを落とさず……ダウンフォース\nを活かして、外側から飛び込んでさらに加速……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not slowing down at that corner… using the downforce‚\ndiving in from the outside and accelerating further…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.900008138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "み、mihoさん、CMとは思えない狂気的な顔で\n車に乗り込んで行くぞ……大丈夫だろうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-miho‚ she’s getting into the car with a look\nof madness on her face… will she be okay…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7333361309,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1166.6613261999998,
          "startTime": 124.0666694642
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.325195299992,
          "startTime": 127.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.4728198369
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-04.m4a",
      "startTime": 131.4728198369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　そんなエンジンを吹かして、一体どうする\nつもり……ほ、ホイルスピンしてるぞ！　凄い煙だ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Revving the engine like that‚ what is she\nplanning… whoa‚ wheels are spinning! So much smoke!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5000048321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7903.0383110000175,
          "startTime": 140.1363818169
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16033.325958299996,
          "startTime": 148.2666694642
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17733.325958300014,
          "startTime": 149.9666694642
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "と思ったら、カーレーサー顔負けの加速ー！？\nエンジンがうなりを上げて、まるで地響きのようだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ acceleration that would put a racer to shame—!?\nThe engine is roaring‚ it feels like the ground is shaking!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333381654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.6333435059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そこからドリフトして……な、なんと一回転したー！\nmiho選手、煙を上げる車から颯爽と降りてきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Drifting there… and‚ whoa‚ she did a full rotation—!\nDriver miho steps coolly out of the smoking car!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.2000027975,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 150.8333361309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "……どうでしたか？\nなかなか迫力のあるドリフトだったでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…How was it?\nThat was a pretty powerful drift‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.1333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.0333435059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "車のメーカーの人達も見に来ているのに\nただスムーズに運転しても、つまらないですからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The car manufacturer people were watching‚\nand it would be boring just to drive smoothly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.1333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "かなりワイルドな運転で驚きました\nでもこの間まで、ひど……いえ個性的な運転だったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised by how wild the driving was.\nBut until recently your driving was terrib… I mean‚ unique.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.3666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.9333435059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "人に病院まで運ばせておいて、その言い草ですか\nまぁ、今回は極力、事前に準備はしておきましたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that any way to talk to someone who drove you to the hospital?\nWell‚ I did prepare as much as possible beforehand this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.4666694642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7399.992624999982,
          "startTime": 183.3333361309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　……これ、さっき走ってた道のマップですか？\nうわ、どう加速してブレーキ踏むか、全部書いてある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? …Is this a map of the road we just drove?\nWhoa‚ it says exactly where to accelerate and brake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.5333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.8000101726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "ある日突然、運転がうまくなる訳もないですし\nとなればもう、丸暗記で対応するしかないですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My driving skills aren’t going to suddenly improve overnight‚\nso I had no choice but to handle it through pure memorization.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.8666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "動画でレーサーの走りを研究して、夜な夜な試しました\nまぁ……このやり方でいくと決めたのは、つい最近です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I studied racer videos and tried them out night after night.\nWell… it was only recently that I decided on this method.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.2000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.7000101726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "どこかの誰かが、情けなくもぶっ倒れたおかげで\n初心者マークのまま、深夜に車を飛ばす羽目になって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to a certain someone collapsing so pathetically‚\nI ended up speeding at midnight with my student plates on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.9000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "そのおかげで運転の感覚も掴めましたし\n何より自信というか、踏ん切りは付きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to that‚ I got a feel for the driving‚\nand more importantly‚ it gave me the resolve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.2333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon",
      "startTime": 228.9000101726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……いやぁ、あの時はご迷惑おかけしました\n少しは俺も役に立てたなら、何よりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… no‚ really‚ I was a burden back then. Sorry.\nI'm glad if I could be of even a little help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.6000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "今回は役に立ちましたが、こんなのはただの偶然です\nいちいち調子に乗らないように",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were helpful this time‚ but that was just luck.\nDon't go letting it get to your head.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.9000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 246.5833435059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、mihoさん。例の自動車メーカーから\nさっき、また連絡をもらいまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ miho. I just heard back\nfrom the car manufacturer again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.5333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんのCM、ワイルドな運転が好評だった\nみたいで、今後も継続的に出演を依頼したいと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems your wild driving in the CM was a hit.\nThey want to request you for ongoing appearances…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.7666694642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……あの運転で褒められるというのは\nなんだか奇妙と言うか、騙されている気分ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… being praised for that kind of driving\nfeels strange‚ almost like I’m being tricked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.2333361309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ。そうだ、せっかく運転にも慣れたことですし\n休みの日にでも、また車で出かけたらどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha. Right‚ since you’re used to driving now‚\nwhy not go for another drive on your day off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 275.8000027975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "それもいいですね……せっかくだから\n昔、葉ちゃんと行った温泉にでも行ってみようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds nice… maybe I’ll even\nvisit the hot spring I went to with Ha-chan back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.0666857403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "今度は全部、自分で運転しないといけませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though this time I’ll have to do all the driving myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.3000264486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "いいじゃないですか。mihoさんが安全運転出来る\nようになったと報告したら、葉さんも喜びますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good. If I tell Ha-chan that you can\ndrive safely now‚ she’ll be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.3000190736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk021.m4a",
      "text": "貴方、また人を危険運転の権化みたいに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ acting like I’m the incarnation of dangerous driving…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.3666931153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk022.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、いいでしょう。では、私は近々\nお休みをいただいて、温泉でゆっくりして来ますので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ fine. I’ll take a break\nsometime soon and relax at the hot spring‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.2333503724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_08_03-mhk023.m4a",
      "text": "その間、あの胃が痛いfranとkanaの面倒を\nどうぞ、よろしくお願いしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so in the meantime‚ please take care of\nthat troublesome fran and kana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 316.3000170391,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}